    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the sought-after 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a documented rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's primary structural concern. The double-VANOS system has been serviced, ensuring precise variable valve timing and linear power delivery. The chassis retains its signature balance thanks to a refreshed suspension setup with polyurethane bushings. While the finish shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is robust, benefiting from a recent cooling system overhaul and rod bearing replacement. An excellent candidate for an enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience without the premium of a collector-grade garage queen.",
      "price": 33800.0,
