      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and presents beautifully as a reliable, high-quality driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with careful use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features well-preserved leather upholstery that has been regularly conditioned; while there is slight natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the interior remains free of tears or odors. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has a comprehensive service history, including recent fluid changes and a fresh set of tires. On the road, the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision, offering a quiet and composed ride. This is an excellent opportunity for a buyer who appreciates a car that has been respected and properly looked after.",
